flowchart TD
    Q[User transcript] --> QP[query_processor.process_query]

    QP --> Alias[Company alias expansion<br/>Hannu InnoTech Hanumayamma]
    Alias --> Topic[Topic regex expansion<br/>sensors PTO dairy specs]
    Topic --> History[search_query += last 2 user<br/>+ last assistant 300 chars]
    History --> Intent{is_conversational}

    Intent -->|yes| Conv[Skip retrieval<br/>CONVERSATIONAL_PROMPT]
    Intent -->|no| EmbedQ[Encode query<br/>all-MiniLM-L6-v2]

    EmbedQ --> Dense[ChromaDB query<br/>n_results 12<br/>filter access_level lte userLevel]

    Dense --> Note1[Note: voice WS hardcodes userLevel=2 INTERNAL]

    Dense --> Rerank[CrossEncoder predict<br/>ms-marco-MiniLM top 8<br/>truncate chunk text 512 chars]

    Rerank --> Context[Take top 3 for LLM prompt<br/>truncate each to 450 chars]

    Context --> LLM[Ollama generate_stream<br/>num_predict 1024 temp 0.4]

    Conv --> LLM

    subgraph HybridGap["Not implemented"]
        BM25[rank_bm25 sparse search]
        RRF[Reciprocal Rank Fusion]
        BM25 -.-> RRF
        RRF -.-> Dense
    end
